{"tid":1120760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4月終於有學生自殺","createTime":"2019-04-23T01:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T01:29:47.000Z","uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"01fee586b6fcc0dbf0ac13e03a458360017bf62b","tid":1120760,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T01:29:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190422/bkn-20190422215553211-0422_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190422%2Fbkn-20190422215553211-0422_00822_001.html&d=%2BBr8udGLiiUmorY0Hhmb0iaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=134c51d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190422/bkn-20190422215553211-0422_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n逸東邨15歲仔墮樓 送院返魂乏術<br />\n<br />\n大嶼山逸東邨祿逸樓，今日(22日)下午5時許，一名姓李(15歲)男童被發現從高處墮下，傳出隆然巨響，多名街坊見狀，慌忙報警求助。救護員接報趕至，男童昏迷被送往北大嶼山醫院搶救，惜至下午5時40分證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n警方封鎖現場，在場沒有檢獲遺書，初步懷疑男童從大廈天台墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定，至於墮樓原因仍有待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好識揀時機, 放完復活節假最後一日先跳<br />\nrip <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}